data.description: Peaceful rancher with great views mature trees and lush greens all around to relax in. One level living with 3 bedrooms 2 car garage hardworking flooring throughout newer kitchen flooring and open and airy living or entertaining space in the living and dining areas.  Cozy family room with brick heart fireplace with access to the deck that surrounds the house and overlooks the serene grounds. The lower level has a bathroom and is waiting your finishing touches. Possibilities are endless!  Great location close to all major highways
